text: U&Eden; is a British free-to-air channel by broadcasted the United Kingdom and Ireland as part of the UKTV channels. The channel was originally launched on 8 March 2004 and relaunched in its current format on 27 January 2009. Eden became free on 7 October 2024 and rebranded to U&Eden; on 16 October 2024. == Related pages == * UKTV == Other websites == * Category:2004 establishments in the United Kingdom Category:British television channels
